org.mitre.tdp.boogie

Interface Transition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Infrastructure, java.io.Serializable

    public interface Transition
extends Infrastructure
    Common interface for transition objects in TDP. This interface is leveraged in downstream code for both fusing transitions across data sources as well as in things like route parsing and other analytics.
